# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/)
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.0.0] - 2025-10-28
### Added
- Unified browser (Spells + Features) with clickable pills and PT/EN search.
- Packs persisted in IndexedDB (offline-ready).
- Print Builder: drag-and-drop reordering, 1â€“2 columns, front/back with mirroring.
- Global preferences (PT/EN language and light/dark/system theme).
- PWA manifest, theme-color, and icons; offline installation and use.

### Improved
- General layout (chips, card grid, floating dock).
- Accessibility: visible focus, skip-to-content, aria labels, and aria-live.
- Print styles (hyphenation, spacing, repeated header).

### Fixed
- Contrast and readability in dark mode (chips, tabs, dock). - Filtering by tags and visual duplication anomalies.